p: These results provided evidence for distinction between brands in glyceride profile ( Figure 1A), borne out by the evidence of subgrouping by type in the glyceride plots of UKB1 ( Figure 1B) and UKB2 ( Figure 1C). UKB3 ( Figure 1D) and UKB4 (not shown) did not show subgrouping. The preparations we investigated comprise combinations of palm oil, sunflower oil, rapeseed oil, coconut oil, soya oil, single cell oil, fish oil and oil from Mortierella alpina.
